	 STAM  R2,R3,FULL2    COPY ARS 2 AND 3 INTO FULL2
	 LM    R8,R9,FULL2    COPY FULL2 INTO GPRS 8 AND 9
	 ABEND 500,DUMP       DUMP CONTENTS OF GPRS AND ARS
*
	 DS    0F
FULL2    DC    D'0'
FULL4    DC    X'00001111'
         DC    X'00022222'
